title: Live from Montreal
description: LIVE IN MONTREAL! Holy cow what a show. Amazing stories, real weirdness, incredible guests. YMIW goes international in Montreal with Eric Andre (the Eric Andre Show, Don't Trust the B in Apartment 23), Jamie Lee (comedy, Kid Farm, Last Comic Standing), Ryan Hamilton (Conan, comedy, the best!), Sean Patton (Conan, comedy central, non-central comedy!) and Pete's Best Worst Friend Chelsea Peretti make for an incredible ep. GET INTO IT! (INSIDE TIP: The story Pete tells is about Nikki Glaser. EVEN MORE AWKWARD!!!)
